events.name: 再びの冒険者ギルドへ

parameters:
Clea, who met Celis the bard, decided to personally defeat
the dragon.

The bard said, 'During the three years that Lady Clea was
gone, her days of training have made her grow both
physically and mentally.'

Bard: And today is the day of her departure. From this day
on, her true adventure begins.

Village Chief's Wife Aruke: Are you really sure about this,
Clea-chan?

Village Chief's Wife Aruke: I understand... At least let me
tidy you up nicely.

Village Chief's Wife Aruke: Before you go to the
Adventurer's Guild, make sure to properly greet your
parents.

Village Chief's Wife Aruke: Alright, I'm done. No matter
what hairstyle you have, you'll always be beautiful.

Clea: Thank you very much. My head feels lighter and
refreshed.
Clea: Well then, I will go and greet my father and mother.

Village Chief's Wife, Arukee Village: Have a safe trip.
Make sure to prepare for your journey on the second floor.

Village Chief's Wife in Arche Village: Take care and have a
safe journey.

Village Chief's Wife in Arche Village: Take care and have a
safe journey.
Clea: I'm sorry for suddenly intruding.

Mayor's Wife of Arche Village: Hehe, you don't have to be
so formal like that.

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: Oh, that's right. Since you're
here, let's have some tea.

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: After returning from the
Adventurer's Guild, I've been training, training,
training... I couldn't calm down.

Mage Relm: Even now, it's still dangerous and keeps me on
edge!

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: When you left here saying you
were going to defeat the dragon, I was worried that you
might try to do everything alone.

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: For me, who has brought so
many friends, it's much more joyful than dragon slaying.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it's rare to come across someone
who I can't help but respect.

Mage Relm: Well, our friends are keeping an eye on things,
so it'll be fine!

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: Oh, that's right. Should I ask
my husband about the honey?

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: I should be cleaning Clea-
chan's new house.
Clea: I-I'm sorry for causing so much trouble.

Arche Village Mayor's Wife: Please come back anytime. Arche
Village is your hometown, after all.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Village Chief's Wife in Arche Village: Take care and have a
safe journey.

Village Chief's Wife, Archee Village: Come back anytime,
you may be a hero, but you're still an important family
member.
Clea: Excuse me, could you please cut my hair?

Archee Village Chief's Wife: Hehe, it's fine. It's an honor
to be able to cut the hair of an imperial hero like you.
Clea: Being called a hero and all...

Archee Village Chief's Wife: You are the pride of this
village. I'm sure your parents are also delighted.
Clea: Yes, thank you very much.

Archee Village Chief's Wife: Yes, it's done. This hairstyle
has really grown on you, hasn't it?

Clea: Thank you very much. I've also grown accustomed to
this hairstyle.
Clea: Well then, I'll go take a look at the new house.
